<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563842>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 9. Kokkocynips difficilis (Ashmead), n. comb., female, SEM pictures. (A) Head dorsal view. (B) Head anterior view. (C) Mesosoma dorsal view (D) Mesosoma lateral view. (E) Propodeum. (F) Metasoma lateral view. (G) Detail of mesoscutellar foveae. (H). Hypopygium." ;
